{"tid":661063,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"Bob Dylan 8月來港開騷！","createTime":"2018-05-11T08:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T11:55:30.000Z","uid":35221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b25175def855be2cafd89bb65518cfdc29916676","tid":661063,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"【事隔7年】諾貝爾獎得主Bob Dylan 8月來港開騷 (13:51)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180510/s00007/d6594566ef992e28e7aebb8804643110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180510%2Fs00007%2Fd6594566ef992e28e7aebb8804643110.jpg&h=108250d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - Bob Dylan將於8月再度來港開騷，樂迷不可錯過。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n現年76歲的美國歌手兼詩人卜戴倫（Bob Dylan），自2016年獲頒諾貝爾文學獎後，再度來港演出，定於8月4日假香港會議展覽中心展覽廳5BC舉行Bob Dylan And His Band Live in Hong Kong 2018演唱會。 Bob Dylan上次在港表演已是2011年，兩場演出全部爆滿。今次票價分1288、988、688及488港元，門票將於下周一（14日）在快達票公開發售。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180510/s00007/1525932002965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180510%2Fs00007%2F1525932002965&d=cvraUpSWqjSd0pn6kM4YLhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=53141df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180510%2Fs00007%2F1525932002965&h=ff8605af\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180510/s00007/1525932002965</a>"},{"pid":"d0ca1e1ec466ae89f2ed564658f4bc92ed392195","tid":661063,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de8600541c9273dd296cb531d1763470ebb94bc","tid":661063,"uid":4383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/